[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare care-coordination assistant decomposes into ten logical stages: enrollment and consent (including caregiver-consent scope), longitudinal-store initialization with cross-system task model, channel entry with disclosure refresh, input safety screening, identity-and-context loading with multi-system-state assembly, conversation handling with cross-system-grounded responses, output safety screening with operational-state-honesty verification, cross-bot routing and human-coordinator handoff, care-team and caregiver reporting with consent enforcement, and audit logging with multi-organization data discipline. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.8 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (cross-system integration substrate, operational task model, threshold-driven proactive engagement, multi-party consent enforcement at the routing layer, and operational-state-honesty discipline).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + CONSENT ──────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolls via discharge workflow,                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    chronic-care-management enrollment, or                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    member-services touchpoint]                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented consent reviewed by legal counsel and     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      clinical leadership                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Channel preferences and quiet hours                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented caregiver(s) with explicit consent scope  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (full visibility, appointments-and-logistics-only,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      none, or custom)                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team-sharing consent (separately collected)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - State-specific consent variations                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent for plan-side data integration where         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      applicable                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed consent record(s); enrollment           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    confirmation; longitudinal-store initialization]        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL STORE + TASK MODEL INIT ──────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-coordination longitudinal store]              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active care plans, with episodes-of-care boundaries │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented caregivers with consent scope            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Channel preferences, quiet hours                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stated language and preferred-name preferences      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history (initially empty)              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Operational-task index (the assistant's working    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      memory of every active referral, prior auth,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      order, scheduled appointment, post-discharge task) │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Operational task model]                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Each task: id, type, source-system, source-system  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      external-id, status, owner, threshold,            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      last-update timestamp, escalation policy          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Task types: referral, prior_auth, dme_order,      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      lab_order, imaging_order, scheduled_appointment,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      post_discharge_followup, transitional_care,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      sdoh_referral, medication_pickup, refill,          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      home_health_order, infusion_order, transport_need, │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      caregiver_communication                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Storage architecture]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Structured data: DynamoDB tables                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation transcript: S3 with vector retrieval  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-system-snapshot cache: DynamoDB with TTL     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - 42 CFR Part 2 information (where applicable):     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      separately keyed and access-controlled             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: longitudinal store ready; task model         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    populated from initial integration sweep]            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CHANNEL ENTRY WITH DISCLOSURE ─────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient or caregiver entry]                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - In-app chat (most common)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - SMS                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Web chat                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Voice channel (where supported)                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver-authenticated channel respects             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      caregiver-specific consent scope                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Bot-initiated entry per protocol]                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduled per coordination protocol with quiet       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      hours and engagement-fatigue mitigation              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Threshold-triggered (stalled referral, overdue       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      task, denied prior auth, appointment with            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      logistical precondition unmet)                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team-flagged tasks                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Disclosure refresh]                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I'm a chat tool, not a person, helping you with     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordination"                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I can pull current state from the systems where     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      your care lives"                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "If anything is urgent or you want a person, I can   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      connect you to a coordinator"                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent acknowledged                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Conversation session bootstrap]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generate session_id                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Capture channel, authentication context,            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      participant identity (patient vs caregiver)          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: session_id, channel, auth context,             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    participant identity, disclosure acknowledged]         │
